text:
Thanks for the birthday card, man!
I loved it so much that I tasted it!
It even came with a present!
I sent you a present too, because
that card was TASTY!

Thanks for the birthday card!
I never knew ya could attach a
present to a card! That's wild, man!
I'm attaching a thank-you present
for you, because now I know how!
I hope ya dig it!

I really liked the present you
sent me, n\0!
I wanted to say thanks sooner, but
I was three bags of chips deep,
and watching TV like it's my job!
Since I'm late, I got you a present!

I didn't expect a birthday card!
From you! For me! On my birthday!
In my mailbox! At my house! Neat!
Since I am now a year older, I shall
endeavor to maintain a level of
maturity heretofore unseen.

Thanks for the birthday card!
That was a real neat thing you
said about how I should have a
happy birthday. So I did it!
I'm gonna work hard to be happy
all year until my next birthday!

I got your birthday card and
I wanted to tell you that I liked it.

I liked it!

Thanks, n\0!
